  "source": "// Demonstrates seiyaku-level metadata controlling the IVM header.\n// - abi_version: syscall policy selection\n// - vector_length: logical SIMD width hint\n// - max_cycles: optional cap for cycle padding/enforcement\n// - zk/vector: set mode bits explicitly\n\nseiyaku MetaDemo {\n  meta {\n    abi_version: 1;\n    vector_length: 8;\n    max_cycles: 2000;\n    zk: true;\n    vector: true;\n  }\n\n  // Contract initializer (run on deploy by the runtime)\n  hajimari() {\n    // Emit vector/zk opcodes so the meta flags are exercised.\n    setvl(8);\n    let _digest = poseidon2(1, 2);\n    let a = 1;\n  }\n}\n",
